{"tid":2155831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府斥「日本跨黨派聯盟」干涉中國內政　被嘲連人家名字都搞錯","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T05:46:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5f19c6afb726cfd1b421c27048da587956b540","tid":2155831,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/港府斥-日本跨黨派聯盟-干涉中國內政-被嘲連人家名字都搞錯/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%A5-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B7%A8%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF-%E8%A2%AB%E5%98%B2%E9%80%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E9%83%BD%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=b0ca2556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%A5-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B7%A8%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E5%B9%B2%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF-%E8%A2%AB%E5%98%B2%E9%80%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E9%83%BD%E6%90%9E%E9%8C%AF%2F&h=9fa1b868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/港府斥-日本跨黨派聯盟-干涉中國內政-被嘲連人家名字都搞錯/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方國安處人員拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、前香港眾志成員周庭等十人。「日本對華政策國會議員聯盟 (Japan Parliamentary Alliance on China, JPAC)」周三（12 日）批評港府以《國安法》侵犯思想自由。當日晚上，港府隨即發聲明「嚴正反駁」，批評「部分日本政客」言論偏頗，干涉中國内政及香港事務。不過該聲明回應的對象卻是「日本跨黨派聯盟」，而沒有提及 JPAC。有網民質疑港府連回應對象名字都弄錯。JPAC 亦在其 twitter 回應指﹕<strong>「我們的正確名字中文是『日本對華政策國會議員聯盟』，僅此告知，請多多指教。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n由於周庭精通日語，經常接受日媒訪問講述香港社運情況，受日本民間奉為「民主女神」，其被捕消息在日本引起廣大迴響。#FreeAgnes（釋放周庭）的 hashtag 亦成為日本 Twitter 熱門話題。日本幾乎所有大媒體等均有報道周庭及黎智英等被捕一事。<br />\n<br />\nJPAC 於上月 29 日成立，由日本跨黨派國會議員組成，成員包括執政自民黨中谷元、長島昭久、有村治子、藤末健三、山田宏，以及在野立憲民主黨的桜井周、國民民主黨的山尾志桜里、維新之會的串田誠一、希望之黨井上一徳等。JPAC 於 12 日發表聲明指，不能接受香港政府侵犯思想自由，呼籲中共和港府根據《中英聯合聲明》承諾的「一國兩制」，履行義務，保障香港市民的自治和自由。聲明又提到，港府推遲立法會選舉，削弱香港穩定繁榮根基的民主進程，呼籲港府恢復被 DQ 候選人的資格、並盡快舉行選舉。"},{"pid":"d8e949277ac9dd0d36c49051b5d840dbee967fbe","tid":2155831,"uid":64337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"港共日日都要柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d2f8e08c8173b6132b47b31409722eb853a578","tid":2155831,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"班AO唔駛去日本勒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac03956707a4b952fe9492322fc7f52b7f8a531","tid":2155831,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b693c6b6201cec62a426f15271806bb908f9abeb","tid":2155831,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑警會唔會有一日冇得去日韓台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d193d73fb5e9a7594da60790e1e4b5fa8fcc70a","tid":2155831,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b693c6b6201cec62a426f15271806bb908f9abeb","tid":2155831,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑警會唔會有一日冇得去日韓台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"台已經冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e495db987b03bb27e29e5d03d0676871376a3be","tid":2155831,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b693c6b6201cec62a426f15271806bb908f9abeb","tid":2155831,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"黑警會唔會有一日冇得去日韓台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla